{
  "texts": [
    "Heuillet et al. [54] utilized the Shapley value to quantify the contributions of each agent in a cooperative MARL environment.",
    "This approach provides a quantitative explanation, enabling a better understanding of the behavior and decision-making process of agents.",
    "Lundberg et al. [22] presented Prescience, an ML approach based on an ensemble model, for predicting the near-term risk of hypoxemia during anesthesia care and explaining the specific factors related to patients and surgeries that contribute to this risk.",
    "To provide real-time explanations, it has developed an effective and theoretically sound ML technique for explaining the importance of individual features in the model's predictions for each patient.",
    "These explanations are presented in concise visualizations for anesthesiologists' use."
  ]
}